            Please consult the priest for the necessary materials required for each function.
            Thakshanai (Dakshina) may be given at the devotee's discretion.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-8 space-y-10">

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--color-ink-mute)] mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-[var(--color-rule)]">At the Temple</h3>
            <div class="divide-y divide-[var(--color-rule)]">
